first_para: Angus Brendan MacNeil (Scottish Gaelic: Aonghas Brianan MacNèill) (born 21 July 1970) is the Scottish National Party (SNP) Member of Parliament (MP) for Na h-Eileanan an Iar.

full.extract:
Angus Brendan MacNeil (Scottish Gaelic: Aonghas Brianan MacNèill) (born 21 July 1970) is the Scottish National Party (SNP) Member of Parliament (MP) for Na h-Eileanan an Iar.
He is the SNP's Westminster portfolio and transport spokesperson.
full.title: Angus MacNeil
